keyFacts: A law enforcement inquiry was conducted for an individual named Tova Noel, born July 27, 1988.

Searches of the NCIC Person Files, Protection Order File, and Interstate Identification Index (III) returned no active warrants, protection orders, or identifiable criminal history records for Tova Noel.
The inquiry was performed by the Federal Bureau of Investigation - New York in conjunction with the New York State Division of Criminal Justice Services.
The document references FBI Case No. 90A-NY-3151227 in relation to the subject Tova Noel.
